{"tid":1748620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26/11 全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利","createTime":"2019-11-23T18:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:53:19.000Z","uid":276382,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"364eb0f0e5ca0be4b01bfec66ae5522dc50126de","tid":1748620,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"黃店與藍店之間總有綠店，不表態、裝作中立。 我們沒有必要跟中共一樣，迫每間公司歸邊。既然深藍老闆要扮作政治中立，就不要以為滅聲、不談政治就是中立，事實是容不下員工的反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n平日琴行歡迎客人、甚至員工試玩樂器，既然琴行要賺黃絲Band 仔的錢，就不應該對他們彈奏《願榮光歸香港》不滿。如不歡迎黃絲客人，罵他們做「曱甴」，不如叫手足直接將琴行加盟藍店。<br />\n<br />\n用音樂感化「偽綠店」，號召各樂手一同到琴行試玩樂器，齊齊演奏《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n不會樂器的朋友歡迎一起詠唱或當樂迷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全城樂手齊心演奏薈通利<br />\n日期：2019年11月26日（星期二）<br />\n時間：7:30pm<br />\n地點：尖沙咀通利琴行<br />\n衣著：做返自己 （宜戴口罩防二噁英）<br />\n大會指定歌曲：《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n結他譜下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guitarians.com%2Fchord%2F76287%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FmqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=aa88932e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guitarians.com/chord/76287/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MwV9Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MwV9Jf.jpg&h=68035d32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"032cb3899daffb74afafaae1a603b5a012269313","tid":1748620,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:05:30.000Z","msg":"推，P牌仔幫手推<br />\n無撚用都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d993590fbd332b31d41efc57957d53c8b675e9","tid":1748620,"uid":93443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{